      "writtenOn": "2020-03-24T19:00:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think expected/actualReturnValue carry the same information as want/got, which is a pretty standard Go idiom. For that reason I\u0027ll stick with the more idiomatic way.\n\nI agree with using more meaningful names if the context is unclear, but I don\u0027t think that\u0027s the case here.",
